title: Sample Book (France), 1940
description: Book with a white cover and "Rodier" printed in red and black letters. Contains sketches of garments and samples of textiles with descriptions and prices.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (France), 1940; Manufactured by Rodier ; cardboard, swatches; H x W x D: 40 x 34.5 x 6 cm (15 3/4 x 13 9/16 x 2 3/8 in.); Gift of William Hardy, Inc.; 1940-103-3
